==English==

{{rank|man's|write|caught|652|below|window|instead|giving}}

===Etymology===
From {{ME.}} ''[[bilooghe]]'' < {{ME.}} ''[[bi]]'' “by” + ''[[looghe]]'' “low”.

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-below.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Preposition===
'''below'''

# [[lower]] in [[spatial]] [[position]] than
#: ''The treasure is buried 2 meters '''below''' the ground.''
# [[lower]] in [[value]] than
#: ''The temperature is '''below''' zero.''
# [[downstream]] of
# [[south]] of
# unsuitable to the [[rank]] or [[dignity]] of
#: ''Such petty behavior is '''below''' me.''

====Synonyms====
*{{italbrac-colon|lower in spatial position than}} [[beneath]], [[under]], [[underneath]]
*{{italbrac-colon|lower in value than}} [[under]]
*{{italbrac-colon|downstream of}} [[downstream]]
*{{italbrac-colon|unsuitable to the rank or dignity of}} [[beneath]]

====Antonyms====
*{{italbrac-colon|lower in spatial position than}} [[above]], [[over]]
*{{italbrac-colon|lower in value than}} [[over]]
*{{italbrac-colon|downstream of}} [[upstream]]


